-0\" role=\"option\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"text\">Rocket Uniface Library 10.4</span></a></li><li><a class=\"dropdown-item\" id=\"bs-select-1-1\" role=\"option\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"text\">Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.0</span></a></li><li><a class=\"dropdown-item\" id=\"bs-select-1-2\" role=\"option\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"text\">Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.1</span></a></li><li><a class=\"dropdown-item\" id=\"bs-select-1-3\" role=\"option\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"text\">Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.1</span></a></li><li><a class=\"dropdown-item\" id=\"bs-select-1-4\" role=\"option\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"text\">Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.0</span></a></li><li><a class=\"dropdown-item\" id=\"bs-select-1-5\" role=\"option\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"text\">Reflection Desktop User Guide (German)</span></a></li><li><a class=\"dropdown-item\" id=\"bs-select-1-6\" role=\"option\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"text\">Secure Host Access FTP Client User Guide (German)</span></a></li><li><a class=\"dropdown-item\" id=\"bs-select-1-7\" role=\"option\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"text\">Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.0</span></a></li><li><a class=\"dropdown-item\" id=\"bs-select-1-8\" role=\"option\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"text\">Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.0</span></a></li><li><a class=\"dropdown-item\" id=\"bs-select-1-9\" role=\"option\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"text\">Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.1</span></a></li><li><a class=\"dropdown-item\" id=\"bs-select-1-10\" role=\"option\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"text\">Reflection FTP Scripting (German) V21.1</span></a></li><li><a class=\"dropdown-item\" id=\"bs-select-1-11\" role=\"option\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"text\">Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.1</span></a></li></ul></div></div></div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-angle-arrow-right\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-angle-arrow-right\"></use></svg></div></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gsr1665702580242.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gsr1665702580242.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gsr1665702580242.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gsr1665702580242\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      \n                          Display\n                        </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Sets the component instance to display-only, meaning that data cannot be modified using structure editor functions. Valid values are <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> (default)\n </p>\n<p class=\"p refsyn\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"A_FORM\",\n            \"MyInstance\",</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"Display=</code> True |\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gsr1665702580242__table_d13028e1_d13029e1_d13030e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gsr1665702580242__table_d13028e1_d13029e1_d13030e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gsr1665702580242__table_d13028e1_d13029e1_d13030e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gsr1665702580242__table_d13028e1_d13029e1_d13030e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gsr1665702580242__table_d13028e1_d13029e1_d13030e1__entry__2\">\n Component instance can be edited using structure editor functions.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gsr1665702580242__table_d13028e1_d13029e1_d13030e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gsr1665702580242__table_d13028e1_d13029e1_d13030e1__entry__2\">Component instance is display-only. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gsr1665702580242__section_rrt_jxv_dxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1038519e120\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gsr1665702580242__p_d111494e1_d111495e1_d111496e1\">When a form instance is display-only, data cannot\n            be modified using structure editor functions. It is still possible to modify data with\n            ProcScript statements, but this is not recommended since it makes maintaining the form\n            more difficult.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gsr1665702580242__p_d111497e1_d111498e1_d111499e1\">For example, the following statement starts a\n            display-only form:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"gsr1665702580242__pre_mfp_kxv_dxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$1 = $1 + 1\nnewinstance \"MYFORM\", \"MYFORM%%$1\", \"DISPLAY=TRUE\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gsr1665702580242__p_d111500e1_d111501e1_d111502e1\">Using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/display</span> switch on the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">run</span> statement is equivalent to setting the property\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">DISPLAY=TRUE</code> for the form.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gsr1665702580242__section_h2w_kxv_dxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1038519e147\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"gsr1665702580242__ul_bcv_lxv_dxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gsr1665702580242__li_d40451e1_d40452e1_d40453e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euw1665702582150.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euw1665702582150.html\" title=\"A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application.\">Form</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613355\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613355\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Display Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Version: Use up/down arrow keys to navigate, Esc to collapse. Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.0 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.1 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.1 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.0 Reflection Desktop User Guide (German) Secure Host Access FTP Client User Guide (German) Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Scripting (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.1 Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.0 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.1 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.1 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.0 Reflection Desktop User Guide (German) Secure Host Access FTP Client User Guide (German) Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Scripting (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.1 Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Display Sets the component instance to display-only, meaning that data cannot be modified using structure editor functions. Valid values are True or False (default) newinstance \"A_FORM\", \"MyInstance\", \"Display= True | False \" Value Description False Component instance can be edited using structure editor functions. True Component instance is display-only. Description When a form instance is display-only, data cannot be modified using structure editor functions. It is still possible to modify data with ProcScript statements, but this is not recommended since it makes maintaining the form more difficult. For example, the following statement starts a display-only form: $1 = $1 + 1 newinstance \"MYFORM\", \"MYFORM%%$1\", \"DISPLAY=TRUE\" Copy Using the /display switch on the run statement is equivalent to setting the property DISPLAY=TRUE for the form. Applies To Form Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}